---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Κλείσε Ραντεβού" active="book">

<main class="pt-32 pb-20 px-4 md:px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<!-- Header Section -->
<div class="mb-12 text-center md:text-left">
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 tracking-tight">Προγραμματισμός Συνεδρίας</h1>
<p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                Επιλέξτε την ημερομηνία και την ώρα που σας εξυπηρετεί για μια εξατομικευμένη διατροφική συμβουλευτική.
            </p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
<!-- Left Column: Calendar Interface -->
<div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-on-surface">Οκτώβριος 2024</h2>
<div class="flex gap-2">
<button class="p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_left</span>
</button>
<button class="p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_right</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Calendar Grid -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-7 gap-2 mb-8">
<!-- Days Header -->
<div class="text-center py-2 text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider">Δευ</div>
<div class="text-center py-2 text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider">Τρι</div>
<div class="text-center py-2 text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider">Τετ</div>
<div class="text-center py-2 text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider">Πεμ</div>
<div class="text-center py-2 text-xs font-bold text-outline uppercase tracking-wider">Παρ</div>
<div class="text-center py-2 text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider">Σαβ</div>
<div class="text-center py-2 text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider">Κυρ</div>
<!-- Calendar Days (Mockup) -->
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-outline-variant opacity-40">26</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-outline-variant opacity-40">27</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-outline-variant opacity-40">28</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-outline-variant opacity-40">29</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-outline-variant opacity-40">30</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-on-surface">1</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-on-surface">2</div>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">3</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">4</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">5</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg shadow-md font-bold">6</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">7</button>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-on-surface font-medium">8</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-on-surface font-medium">9</div>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">10</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">11</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">12</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">13</button>
<button class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm">14</button>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-on-surface font-medium">15</div>
<div class="aspect-square flex items-center justify-center text-on-surface font-medium">16</div>
</div>
<!-- Time Slots -->
<div class="mt-8 border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-8">
<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">schedule</span>
                        Διαθέσιμες Ώρες (6 Οκτωβρίου)
                    </h3>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
<button class="py-3 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all">09:00</button>
<button class="py-3 px-4 bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-lg text-sm font-bold shadow-sm">10:30</button>
<button class="py-3 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all">12:00</button>
<button class="py-3 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all">14:00</button>
<button class="py-3 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all">16:30</button>
<button class="py-3 px-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/30 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-all">18:00</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right Column: Form -->
<div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-8">
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-6">Στοιχεία Επικοινωνίας</h2>
<form class="space-y-6">
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">person</span>
                                Όνομα
                            </label>
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-lg p-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all text-on-surface" placeholder="Εισάγετε το ονοματεπώνυμό σας" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">phone</span>
                                Τηλέφωνο
                            </label>
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-lg p-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all text-on-surface" placeholder="+30 690 0000000" type="tel"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">medical_services</span>
                                Σκοπός Επίσκεψης
                            </label>
<select class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-lg p-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:bg-surface-container-highest transition-all text-on-surface appearance-none">
<option>Απώλεια Βάρους</option>
<option>Αθλητική Διατροφή</option>
<option>Κλινική Διατροφή (Παθήσεις)</option>
<option>Διατροφική Εκπαίδευση</option>
<option>Άλλο</option>
</select>
</div>
<div class="pt-4">
<button class="w-full bg-primary text-on-primary py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-all active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2" type="submit">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">event_available</span>
                                Επιβεβαίωση Ραντεβού
                            </button>
<p class="text-xs text-center text-outline mt-4 leading-relaxed">
                                Με την επιβεβαίωση, αποδέχεστε την Πολιτική Απορρήτου και τους Όρους Χρήσης της Organic Nutrition.
                            </p>
</div>
</form>
</div>
<!-- Info Card -->
<div class="bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-start">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">info</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold mb-1">Πληροφορίες Ραντεβού</h4>
<p class="text-sm opacity-90">Οι συνεδρίες πραγματοποιούνται είτε δια ζώσης στο γραφείο μας είτε μέσω βιντεοκλήσης. Θα λάβετε email επιβεβαίωσης εντός 24 ωρών.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</Layout>
